It is with sadness that we share with you that our founder and friend, Timothy J. Keller passed away in the morning of May 19, 2023 at the age of 72, trusting in the sure and certain hope of the resurrection. Please join us in prayer for his family as they go through the grieving process. While our hearts are heavy with the news of Tim’s death, we know he is rejoicing with his Savior in heaven.

Kathy and Michael Keller share a special Christmas message for you today as you experience the joy and meaning of Christ’s birth.

2023 has brought many changes and transitions in all our lives. Here at Gospel in Life we continue to be grateful for the ways God has used your faithful support to bring about gospel transformation in people’s lives all over the world. On behalf of my family and the Gospel in Life Team—thank you for helping us share the good news of Christ’s love this past year. It is our privilege to serve you through this ministry!

Please watch this short video we’ve recorded to share how thankful I am for your partnership in ministry, and how we believe God is calling the ministry of Gospel in LIfe to move forward in the coming year. – Kathy Keller
